scopecontent.p:
The Waddington Archive consists of scientific notebooks and bundles of
		  notes; manuscripts and typescripts of essays, articles and larger works;
		  photographic illustrations for publications; correspondence with publishers;
		  correspondence with scientific journals; scientific correspondence;
		  correspondence with societies; material relating to meetings and conferences;
		  papers and books for review; University of Edinburgh files; and other
		  miscellaneous files. The Archive also contains confidential personal files
		  which are not available for consultation until 2025.
